Security Professionals - Retail Environment in Sherman Oaks <br>
<br>
JOIN US FOR OUR HIRING EVENT!<br>
DATE: March 22nd<br>
TIME: 9:00am - 3:00pm<br>
LOCATION: 15301 Ventura Blvd, Sherman Oaks CA 91403<br>
MEETING LOCATION: Security Office & Information on the North Plaza<br>
CONTACT: Blanca Ojeda (818)382-4144<br>
PARKING: Parking will be validated. Please enter the parking structure through the Camarillo Street entrance<br>
<br>
Allied Universal is currently looking for motivated Security Professionals interested in working in a retail environment. If you like public interaction and have great customer service skills, this position is for you!<br>
<br>
Qualifications/Requirements:<br>
*High school diploma or equivalent required<br>
*Must have a CA Guard License or have the ability to obtain one<br>
*Must possess effective written and oral communication and interpersonal skills with ability to deal with all levels of personnel and the general public in a professional and effective manner; must be able to use initiative and independent judgment within established guidelines<br>
*Must be able to frequently prepare written reports and logs in neat, legible handwriting<br>
*Must display exceptional customer service and communication skills<br>
*Intermediate computer skills to utilize innovative, wireless technology<br>
*Read, understand and clearly speak English; constantly use speech and hearing (correctable to normal level required) in communicating with public/co-workers, giving and receiving instructions, using phones<br>
*Must be able to handle pressure of working with high volume general public (constantly to occasionally depending on assignment)<br>
<br>
Apply online @ www.aus.com/careers, then enter one of the requisition ID numbers listed below in the search keyword area:<br>
<br>
&#61558;	Security Shift Supervisor - requisition ID# 2017-114393<br>
&#61558;	Retail Security Professional - requisition ID# 2017-114399<br>
&#61558;	Dispatch - requisition ID# 2017-114395<br>
&#61558;	Patrol - requisition ID# 2017-114397<br>
    </section>

